    "While there are a few approaches combining ML or DL with XAI and in the case of the last mentioned study (Alsuradi et al., 2020) even findings from typical conventional EEG analyses could be corroborated, to the best of our knowledge, we are the first to use this combination of methods to detect ERP components objectively."
